thread.title: BRIEF-Greensky Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $100 Mln

title: BRIEF-Greensky Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $100 Mln
text:
April 27 (Reuters) -
* GREENSKY INC FILES FOR IPO OF UP TO $100 MILLION – SEC FILING
* GREENSKY INC SAYS IT INTENDS TO APPLY TO HAVE ITS COMMON STOCK LISTED UNDER THE SYMBOL “GSKY”
* GREENSKY INC SAYS GOLDMAN SACHS & CO. LLC, J.P. MORGAN, MORGAN STANLEY ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO
* GREENSKY INC SAYS BOFA MERRILL LYNCH, CITIGROUP, CREDIT SUISSE ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO
* GREENSKY INC SAYS SUNTRUST ROBINSON HUMPHREY, RAYMOND JAMES, SANDLER O’NEILL + PARTNERS, L.P ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO
* GREENSKY INC SAYS FIFTH THIRD SECURITIES, GUGGENHEIM SECURITIES ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO
* GREENSKY INC SAYS PROPOSED IPO PRICE IS AN ESTIMATE SOLELY FOR CALCULATING SEC REGISTRATION FEE Source text: bit.ly/2KlqOqU
